summary:
- **Type**: Performance Rights Issuance  
- **Total Issued**: 67,050,000 performance rights (CY5AJ)  
- **Issue Date**: 11 July 2025  
- **Recipients**:  
  - **Key Management Personnel (KMP)**: 40,250,000 (including 12M each to David Southam and Ernest Mast)  
  - **Employees/Consultants**: 29.05M (under Listing Rule 7.2 Exception 13)  
- **Post-Issue Unquoted Securities**:  
  - Performance Rights (CY5AJ): 87,978,809  
  - Ordinary Shares (CY5): 1,063,262,178 (quoted)  
- **Terms**: Linked to employee incentive scheme (terms via [provided URL](https://cdn-api.markitdigital.com/apiman-gateway/ASX/asx-research/1.0/file/2924-02936427-6A1260151&v=4a466cc3f89))  

**Material Impact**: Dilution from performance rights issuance (6.3% of existing ordinary shares), primarily to KMP. No immediate trading impact (unquoted).
